---

This plugin reimplements, as a prompt pipeline, the methodology of STORM
(Synthesis of Topic Outlines through Retrieval and Multi-perspective Question
asking) by the Stanford OVAL Lab — https://github.com/stanford-oval/storm
(MIT License), described in "Assisting in Writing Wikipedia-like Articles From
Scratch with Large Language Models" (NAACL 2024, arXiv:2402.14207). It also
incorporates the 4-prompt adaptation popularized by Nav Toor (@heynavtoor).
This plugin is an independent work and is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Stanford University.
